<p></p>About Debbie Ohi<p>Debbie Ridpath Ohi writes and illustrates books for young people. Recent illustration projects for Simon &#38; Schuster Children's include books by Judy Blume and Michael Ian Black. Her blog for children's book writers &#38; illustrators: Inkygirl.com. On Twitter: @inkyelbows</p>Web &#124; Twitter &#124; Facebook &#124; Google+ &#124; Flickr &#124; More <br/><div class="clearfix"></div>]]></description>
